    public class FhirMessageConverter
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.springframework.http.converter.HttpMessageConverter
    Implementation of HttpMessageConverter that is used by SpringBoot to serialize responses from APIs in FHIR JSON or XML. Uses the HAPI libraries to serialize.
